== 不同國家比薩差距的可能成因研究 ==
雖然PISA和TIMSS的官員和研究人員通常不假設國家之間、學生成績的龐大而穩定的差異，自2000以來，在比薩和TIMSS結果的差異及其原因的文獻已經出現。<ref>Hanushek, Eric A., and Ludger Woessmann. 2011. "The economics of international differences in educational achievement." In ''Handbook of the Economics of Education'', Vol. 3, edited by Eric A. Hanushek, Stephen Machin, and Ludger Woessmann. Amsterdam: North Holland: 89–200.</ref>來自比薩的數據提供了一些經濟學家，尤其是Eric Hanushek，Ludger Woessmann，Heiner Rindermann，Stephen J. Ceci，與學生和經濟發展之間的關系的書籍和文章材料<ref>Hanushek, Eric; Woessmann, Ludger (2008), [http://www.citizing.org/data/projects/highered/The%20Role%20of%20Cognitive%20Skills%20in%20Economic%20Development%20Hanushek_Woessmann%202008.pdf "The role of cognitive skills in economic development"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.citizing.org/data/projects/highered/The%20Role%20of%20Cognitive%20Skills%20in%20Economic%20Development%20Hanushek_Woessmann%202008.pdf |date=20170707214247 }} (PDF), ''Journal of Economic Literature'', '''46''' (3): 607–668, doi:[https://doi.org/10.1257%2Fjel.46.3.607 10.1257/jel.46.3.607]</ref>的民主化，和健康<ref>Rindermann, Heiner; Ceci, Stephen J (2009), "Educational policy and country outcomes in international cognitive competence studies", ''Perspectives on Psychological Science'', '''4''' (6): 551–577, doi:[https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1745-6924.2009.01165.x 10.1111/j.1745-6924.2009.01165.x]</ref>；以及高風險考試這種單一的教育因素的作用<ref>Bishop, John H (1997), [http://digitalcommons.ilr.cornell.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1142&context=cahrswp "The effect of national standards and curriculum-based exams on achievement"] {{Wayback|url=http://digitalcommons.ilr.cornell.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1142&context=cahrswp |date=20171108123331 }}, ''American Economic Review'', '''87''' (2): 260–264</ref>，有或沒有私立學校，和效果和跟蹤時間的能力。<ref>Hanushek, Eric; Woessmann, Ludger (2006), [http://www.econstor.eu/bitstream/10419/18779/1/cesifo1_wp1415.pdf "Does educational tracking affect performance and inequality? Differences-in-differences evidence across countries"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.econstor.eu/bitstream/10419/18779/1/cesifo1_wp1415.pdf |date=20170706145804 }}(PDF), ''Economic Journal'', '''116''' (510): C63–C76, doi:[https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1468-0297.2006.01076.x 10.1111/j.1468-0297.2006.01076.x]</ref>

